---
/*
  Site footer.
  Three columns, each a label + brand mark:
    - Left:   "Built for"             → Reach University (mode-aware logo)
    - Center: "Made with ♥ on Astro by" → The Lossless Group (inlined SVG)
    - Right:  "An Astro Knots project"  → Astro Knots
  Mode-aware Reach mark (light SVG / dark + vibrant white SVG).
  Lossless Group is inlined so the dark wordmark glyphs can be retinted in
  dark/vibrant modes via var(--color-text).

  Pattern stolen from sites/fullstack-vc/src/components/basics/Footer.astro,
  retokenized for Reach's theme.css (var(--color-*), --font-mono, --color-accent).
*/
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

